Package: appliance-manager
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: DiskWeaver Project <noel.phillips@gmail.com>
Depends: cockpit-bridge
Description: Cockpit UI for appliance-level services (Garage buckets/keys, and future components)
 Appliance Manager complements DiskWeaver (disk pooling) with the
 appliance-level services built on top of it -- starting with Garage
 S3 bucket/access-key management, with Samba/NFS/rsync management
 planned. Exposed over a Unix-socket HTTP API and a Cockpit plugin.
 Assumes Garage itself is already installed/configured (see
 provision/provision.sh) -- not expressed as a dpkg dependency since
 Garage isn't installed via apt/dpkg.
